text: Dashu may refer to: *Dashu (solar term) (大暑), the 12th solar term of the traditional East Asian calendars *Dashu District (大樹區), a district of Kaohsiung, Taiwan ==Townships in China== *Dashu Township, Gansu (大树乡), in Dongxiang Autonomous County, Gansu *Dashu Township, Jiangxi (大树乡), in Duchang County, Jiangxi ==Towns in China== *Dashu, Anhui (大墅), in Quanjiao County, Anhui *Dashu, Chongqing (大树), in Fengjie County, Chongqing *Dashu, Shandong (大束), in Zoucheng, Shandong *Dashu, Dazhou (大树), in Dazhou, Sichuan *Dashu, Hanyuan County (大树), in Hanyuan County, Sichuan *Dashu, Zhejiang (大墅), in Chun'an County, Zhejiang ==See also== *Shu (disambiguation) for a list of states in Chinese history called "Da Shu" or "Great Shu"
title: Dashu
